\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of me renting my house and owning a house\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition: Can we just be honest\'85there is a difference in the way we treat something depending on whether we rent it own it.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The same is true with cars right?  How many of you have done things in rental cars that you would never do with your own car.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Maybe you\'92ve rented a house before\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(need a few more illustration here)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  While renting most things isn\'92t bad and is a natural progression in most areas of our lives, renting the church is a problem.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When people rent the church they treat it very differently than people that own the church.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And as we said earlier, when you rent something you treat it very differently than when you own it. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(walk through the different mentalities of the two people with a CHART)\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters talk about RIGHTS while Owners talk about RESPONSIBILITIES\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters talk about what they GET while Owners talk about what they GIVE\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters USE a facility or org while Owners INVEST in a facility or org\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters stay until find they find something BETTER while Owners \'85 not sure here\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters do the bare minimum while Owners do what needs to be done no matter the cost\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters are TEMPORARY while Owners are more PERMANENT.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters call someone else while Owners fix it themselves\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters point out trash on the floor while owners pick it up\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renters talk about the churches problems while Owners talk about our problems with solutions.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition: Now what I hear from people about this is that this is about maturity and it\'92s part of a process.  That renting, much like maybe buying a home, is a step towards following God.  So today I want to look at the very first church and talk where renters are in the church\'85because they are in the Bible.  \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Acts 2 is when the first church started and it is at it\'92s most pure state.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to look at how it all began\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 40\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub With many other words he warned them; and he pleaded with them, \'93Save yourselves from this corrupt generation.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is every pastors job right here\'85to warn and plead.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And in the next few weeks this is going to be me hopefully\'85a little in your face, a little pushy on some stuff I\'92m not normally as pushy as this, but it is because I believe you are made for more than just renting Jesus and His church.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 41\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Those who accepted his message were baptized, and about three thousand were added to their number\'a0that day.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So there is a brand new movement \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}3000 people had a life changing event\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now what do you think their response was?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is what it says\'85.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 42\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub They added an appointment to their schedules for roughly once a week as long as it wasn\'92t vacation time, the lake wasn\'92t calling their name, it wasn\'92t raining, they liked the music, or there wasn\'92t something better going on.  \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That\'92s not really what it says\'85but that is what happens all the time.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And I\'92m not talking about people who are trying to figure the whole God thing out\'85if that\'92s you you\'92re golden!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re here and not a Christian we\'92re not talking about you at all\'85we\'92re glad you\'92re here and hope you come back.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But those who say they\'92ve had a life changing moment where they gave their life, not just their Sunday mornings, to Jesus.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is what it really says\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 42\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub They devoted themselves to the apostles\'92 teaching\'a0and to fellowship, to the breaking of bread\'a0and to prayer.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is one of the problems with technology\'85there are too many people who think if they hear the sermon they went to church. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is nothing further from the truth!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is clear the teaching is one part but also the fellowship, prayer together, communion\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f4\b \cf3 Transition:  Again, some of you who are renting would say, that is what I do\'85but it doesn\'92t have to be every week come on\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 46\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Every day they continued to meet together in the temple courts.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do you see the different mentality?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How does once a week sound now?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The crazy part is even once a week has become problematic for many.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For people that are renting there are a number of issues with even once a week!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There\'92s the lake\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Vacations\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Rainy days\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Days I want to sleep in\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s too hard to get the kids up\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My spouse doesn\'92t want to come\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f4\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is not a situation issue but a devotion issue!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf2 Illustration of me offering you a $1 million if you show up at 7am next week.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quit blaming your kids, weather, jobs, and everything else when it is devotion issue not a situational issue\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 They broke bread\'a0in their homes and ate together with glad and sincere hearts,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 47\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub praising God and enjoying the favor of all the people.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They even had small groups!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So they met daily for church and then met together for dinner!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 And the Lord added to their number\'a0daily those who were being saved.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the movement that changed the world\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is the reason you are sitting in here right now\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because of group of people, several thousand got together and OWNED IT!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They weren\'92t renting out their faith and hoping something rubbed off on them.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  As I said though, we see renting in the church in scripture\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not mentioned in a positive light though but as a call back to what they already know and did before\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can read 1 Corinthians and see all of the issues of people renting the church and making it about them and what they want and don\'92t want.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It even gets so bad that in the book of Hebrews he has to call them back to the most basic thing\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 25\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub not giving up meeting together,\'a0as some are in the habit of doing, but encouraging one another\'97and all the more as you see the Day approaching.  Heb 10:23-25\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is what I want you to see.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Renting the Church is not part of your growth process, but a relapse in your relationship with God.  (make sound better)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Transition:  I want everyone in here who says \'96 I\'92m a Christian, to OWN IT!\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For us a Church I want to talk about 3 specific areas I believe all Christians need to own and the first one is the one we\'92ve used today primarily which is attendance.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What that means is you commit to be here weekly\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Someone will get upset and think God is taking attendance and if that is what you\'92re thinking you\'92ve missed the whole point of today\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Attendance doesn\'92t change how God see\'92s us, it changes how we see God!  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t own what you don\'92t attend.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So I\'92m asking you to commit to attending this series and the next one and allow God to change you and how you see Him.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you imagine with me for a second if the local church just in Glasgow had the same passion and devotion that the first church in the book of Acts? \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The church in America doesn\'92t have a lack of God problem, we have a lack of passion and commitment problem and it start with us, not them!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have to quit pointing the figure at culture and starting allowing God to change us from renters to owners!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Benediction\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You were created for more than simple agreement on issues.  You were create to be a part of something bigger than yourself.  You were created to be a part of a movement of God that transcends the normal into the extraordinary.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
